http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: South Carolina Academic Standards for the Visual and Performing Arts - Media Arts

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: Education systems in the United States have long recognized the need for national standards to provide the basis for a common curriculum and academic programs throughout the country. The South Carolina academic standards for Media Arts are new to South Carolina's academic standards for the Visual and Performing Arts. Studies in media arts utilize many of the elements and principles from other arts disciplines. Original media artworks reflect the aesthetics that are embedded in the visual and performing arts.
